{
  "texts": [
    "In the injection algorithm outlined in Algorithm 1, we set the number of unique perturbations per class, N w, to 1 for AGNews and IMDb, and 10 for NI Polarity.",
    "The threshold t, w min and w max are fixed at 0.01, 10 and 10, respectively.",
    "We use 4-bit models and fine-tune them with a Q-LoRA rank of 16 due to computational constraints.",
    "And we find that the Phi3-medium model does not converge on the clean dataset at rank 16, so we report its results at rank 128, where it performs adequately.",
    "All our experiments were run using the PyTorch library and a single A100-80GB GPU."
  ]
}